
msgid "Fullcone NAT"
msgstr "全锥形 NAT"

msgid "Global gate for SONiC-style fullcone NAT. When enabled, each zone can individually activate fullcone in its settings."
msgstr "SONiC 全锥形 NAT 全局总开关。开启后，每个区域可在各自设置中单独启用全锥形 NAT。"

msgid "Enable fullcone NAT for this zone. Requires the global Fullcone NAT gate to be enabled in General Settings. Use \"Fullcone protocols\" and \"Fullcone source IPs\" in Advanced Settings to restrict scope."
msgstr "为此区域启用全锥形 NAT。需要在常规设置中开启全局全锥形 NAT 总开关。可在高级设置中通过「全锥形协议」和「全锥形源 IP」限制范围。"

msgid "Fullcone protocols"
msgstr "全锥形协议"

msgid "Restrict fullcone NAT to specific L4 protocols. When empty, all protocols use fullcone. Recommended: select only UDP for gaming/P2P use cases."
msgstr "将全锥形 NAT 限制为特定的四层协议。留空则所有协议均使用全锥形 NAT。建议：游戏和 P2P 场景下仅选择 UDP。"

msgid "Fullcone source IPs"
msgstr "全锥形源 IP"

msgid "Restrict fullcone NAT to specific LAN source IP addresses or CIDR subnets. When empty, all source IPs use fullcone. Example: 192.168.1.100 or 192.168.1.0/24"
msgstr "将全锥形 NAT 限制为特定的局域网源 IP 地址或 CIDR 子网。留空则所有源 IP 均使用全锥形 NAT。示例：192.168.1.100 或 192.168.1.0/24"

msgid "All protocols"
msgstr "所有协议"

msgid "All source IPs"
msgstr "所有源 IP"
